query:
SELECT
                guilds.id,
                guilds.name,
                guilds.description,
                guilds.icon,
                guilds.banner,
                guilds.owner_id,
                guilds.flags,
                guilds.vanity_url,
                (SELECT COUNT(*) FROM members WHERE guild_id = guilds.id) AS "member_count!"
            FROM
                guilds
            WHERE
                EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM members WHERE members.id = $1 AND members.guild_id = guilds.id)
                AND ($2::BIGINT[] IS NULL OR guilds.id = ANY($2::BIGINT[]))
